name: The vision of Innekouzou
description:
Innekouzou was a West African Dogon woman diviner in the mid-1900s who made detailed observations of Sirius B, a star impossible to detect with the unaided human eye.

This NFT recreates the experience of Innekouzou’s vision, entering the blackness of her inner imaginal worlds that form a starscape and then the Dogon symbol for Sirius B. Innekouzou then emerges from her meditative trance and repeats this journey, deepening her mystic knowledge with each completion of this recursive sequence.
